name: Honey on Body - Concept

Lets you make girls covered in honey (and sometimes honey slimes if combined with other LoRAs).

Trained off of AOM3A1 on a dataset of 53 hand-filtered images scraped from Gelbooru. May not work well on other models.

Due to the dataset used, subjects may hold jars of honey unprompted. Simply place "holding" and "pouring onto self" in the negative prompt to resolve this issue.

LoRA used in 3rd sample image is https://civitai.com/models/11458/colorful-slime-girl-lora.
